## Performance Optimization

PhoneInput has expensive module-level array operations running on every import.

**Issue**: Lines 260-262, 254-258 create 490+ element array spreads, iterations, filtering on module load.

**Current**:
```typescript
const COMMON_DIAL_CODES = new Set(COMMON_COUNTRIES.map((c) => c.dialCode));
const DIAL_CODE_TO_COUNTRY: Record<string, CountryCode> = {};
for (const c of [...COMMON_COUNTRIES, ...ALL_COUNTRIES]) { /* ... */ }
```

**Fix**: Pre-compute as static object or lazy-initialize:
```typescript
const DIAL_CODE_TO_COUNTRY: Record<string, CountryCode> = {
  "55": "BR",
  "1": "US",
  // ... pre-computed mappings
};
```

