## Issue
invalidateCachePrefix strips only trailing numeric IDs with regex /\/\d+$/, missing sub-resource patterns like /api/visits/123/medications.

## Severity
P2 IMPORTANT - Mutations on sub-resources may not invalidate parent resource caches, leading to stale data.

## Location
